reviews-and-testimonials/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.instagram.com/facetoface_cincoranch/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.mapquest.com/us/texas/face-to-face-spa-431256801"},{"type":"url","url":"https://facetofacespa.com/cinco-ranch/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Hydrafacial&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX"},{"type":"url","url":"https://local.yahoo.com/info-229857630-face-to-face-spa-cinco-ranch-katy/"},{"type":"url","url":"https://www.realself.com/find/Texas/Katy/HydraFacial"},{"type":"url","url":"https://stg-facetofacespa.globenetix.com/cinco-ranch/"}]}},{"id":"tco_81829589-fdbc-90b2-a795-57c4377490d8_call-074cd68f-7187-415d-9a03-7d89d82f7bb4-3","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"tco_81829589-fdbc-90b2-a795-57c4377490d8_call-074cd68f-7187-415d-9a03-7d89d82f7bb4-4","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"id":"tco_81829589-fdbc-90b2-a795-57c4377490d8_call-074cd68f-7187-415d-9a03-7d89d82f7bb4-5","summary":[],"type":"reasoning","status":"completed"},{"content":[{"type":"output_text","text":"**Top-rated HydraFacial providers in the Katy/Houston area (west Houston suburbs) include MedSpa at Villagio, Face to Face Spa (Cinco Ranch), SkinSpirit Katy, Luminous MediSpa, and 4Ever Glow Salon & MedSpa, based on review aggregates, awards, and mentions.**[[1]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Hydrafacial&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)[[2]](https://medspaatvillagio.com/)\n\n“Best” is subjective and depends on factors like your skin goals (e.g., hydration, acne, anti-aging), provider expertise, pricing, and personal experience—always verify current Google/Yelp ratings, confirm they offer official HydraFacial treatments, and schedule a consultation. Here are standout options from recent searches:\n\n- **MedSpa at Villagio (Katy)**: Frequently highlighted on Yelp lists for HydraFacial. Two-time Image Skincare Medspa of the Year winner; recently recognized as Best of Katy 2026 in the Medical Spa category. Strong reviews praise friendly staff, results from facials/laser/Botox, and a relaxing environment. Location: 22764 Westheimer Pkwy, Suite 690, Katy.[[2]](https://medspaatvillagio.com/)[[3]](https://www.facebook.com/medspaatvillagio17/)\n\n- **Face to Face Spa (Cinco Ranch, Katy)**: Tops Yelp searches for HydraFacial with a 4.9/5 rating (35+ reviews). Clients note clean facilities, knowledgeable estheticians, great service for medi-facials (including HydraFacial with dermaplaning), and visible glow/radiance. Positive mentions of friendly staff and effective treatments.[[1]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Hydrafacial&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)[[1]](https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Hydrafacial&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)\n\n- **SkinSpirit Katy**: Premier medical spa chain offering facials/HydraFacial alongside Botox/fillers/microneedling. Emphasizes expert providers, safe/noticeable results, and personalized care in a trusted setting.[[4]](https://www.skinspirit.com/locations/katy)\n\n- **Other strong mentions**: Luminous MediSpa (Katy/Fulshear area, positive professionalism/hygiene feedback and awards recognition for HydraFacial); 4Ever Glow Salon & MedSpa (Katy, client testimonials on transformative HydraFacial results); Ageless MedSpa Katy and 4Ever Young (direct HydraFacial offerings).[[5]](https://luminousmedispa.com/hydra-facial/)[[6]](https://luminousmedispa.com/)\n\n**Recommendations**: Check recent Google, Yelp, or RealSelf reviews for the latest ratings/photos, as they can fluctuate. Look for providers certified in HydraFacial (official equipment/training matters for results/safety). Many offer packages or memberships. Consult a provider to match the treatment to your skin type/concerns. Prices typically range $150–$300+ per session depending on add-ons.[[7]](https://www.realself.com/find/Texas/Katy/HydraFacial)\n\nFor the most current info, search Google Maps for “HydraFacial near Katy TX” or visit provider sites directly. If you have specific preferences (e.g., budget, focus on acne vs. anti-aging), more tailored suggestions are possible!","logprobs":[],"annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Hydrafacial&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX","start_index":259,"end_index":335,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://medspaatvillagio.com/","start_index":335,"end_index":371,"title":"2"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://medspaatvillagio.com/","start_index":1058,"end_index":1094,"title":"2"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.facebook.com/medspaatvillagio17/","start_index":1094,"end_index":1145,"title":"3"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Hydrafacial&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX","start_index":1482,"end_index":1558,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.yelp.com/search?find_desc=Hydrafacial&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX","start_index":1558,"end_index":1634,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.skinspirit.com/locations/katy","start_index":1850,"end_index":1898,"title":"4"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://luminousmedispa.com/hydra-facial/","start_index":2210,"end_index":2258,"title":"5"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://luminousmedispa.com/","start_index":2258,"end_index":2293,"title":"6"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.realself.com/find/Texas/Katy/HydraFacial","start_index":2692,"end_index":2751,"title":"7"}]}],"id":"msg_81829589-fdbc-90b2-a795-57c4377490d8","role":"assistant","type":"message","status":"completed"}],"parallel_tool_calls":true,"previous_response_id":null,"reasoning":{"effort":"low","summary":"detailed"},"temperature":0.7,"text":{"format":{"type":"text"}},"tool_choice":"auto","tools":[{"type":"web_search","search_context_size":"medium"}],"top_p":0.95,"usage":{"input_tokens":13313,"input_tokens_details":{"cached_tokens":6976},"output_tokens":1492,"output_tokens_details":{"reasoning_tokens":828},"total_tokens":14805,"num_sources_used":0,"num_server_side_tools_used":6,"cost_in_usd_ticks":430464500,"server_